#  AR Solar System Project

An Augmented Reality (AR) application developed using Unity and Vuforia for the course **Image Processing (AI 306)**.

The project visualizes the solar system in 3D using image target recognition, allowing users to interact with planets and view detailed information through a modern UI.

---

##  Project Overview

This AR system enables users to:
- Scan predefined image targets
- Render realistic 3D planets in real time
- Interact with virtual objects
- View information about each planet through UI

---

##  Technologies Used

- Unity Engine
- Vuforia Engine (AR SDK)
- C# Programming Language
- Image Processing Concepts


